data.title: DS Fantasy Eurovision 89: Welcome to Le Hurel - this time it's personal - Page 68
data.meta_description: I love CofC, although I never do well. My Germany win, which is still the biggest winner in 83 contest based on points did so poorly.
data.text:
In your time playing DSFE, have you:

* Qualified through a round - Yes

* Reached a final - Yes

* Got two or more countries into a final - Yes. The last time we submitted our own recaps in 81. NZ & Kazakhstan.

* Finished top 10 - Yes. Twice.

* Finished top 10 with more than one entry in the same contest No. Although 8th and 11th with NZ & Kazakhstan in 81 came close.

* Held a record finish for a country - No. But Bosnia has made one Final in the last 30 contests and that was my doing, so that feels like some kind of special record.

* Won a quarter final - No

* Won the QF, SF and final - No

* Received a set of 12 points in the final - Yes

* Suffered a voting collapse - Yes. This contest, 4th in the QF to NQ in the SF.

* Finished last - Not in the Final. 2 lasts in the SFs and 3 times in the QFs.

* Entered a song including some rap - Yes. Ellyland - Bedroom had a little rap breakdown.

* Sent a song you now seriously wish you'd never heard in your entire life - Yes. The two times I had to endure the Northern Ireland experience.

* Gone out completely in the quarter finals No.

* Held a record low finish for a country Yes. Moldova - 24th in the QF. Western Asia - 22nd in the QF and joint lowest points with 5. Romania - 21st in the QF.

* Entered a song that you thought was going to do well but failed miserably - Yes. Many times.

* Chose an artist for the first time that has since been brought back - Yes. Marina Viskovic - I crashed out in the QFs with slutpop and the bitch went to the Final in the next contest with a dirge.

* Sent an act that has gone to ESC or a NF after picking them - Yes. Ellyland was in the early shortlist for the German NF this year.

2

Oh this looks fun

* Qualified through a round

Yup, not as often as I'd thought I would but even so.

* Reached a final

34/121. That's awful isn't it

* Got two or more countries into a final

Tallinn - 2, Lisbon - 2, Horny Bar **** - 2, Hell (I think - wiki on mobile isn't very clear) - 2, Odessa - 2, Douglas - 2

* Finished top 10

Can do better than that - I've come in every top 10 position at least once.

* Finished top 10 with more than one entry in the same contest

2nd & 7th in Lisbon. My peak.

* Held a record finish for a country

Um, not sure. Two wins so there's that.

* Won a quarter final

I've won 6 of the things

* Won the QF, SF and final

SIGRID

* Received a set of 12 points in the final

Er, yeah.

* Suffered a voting collapse

Vote collapse? I've gone from third to fifth to last. Beat that. #ruthwasrobbed

* Finished last

Just a few times...

* Entered a song including some rap

No

* Sent a song you now seriously wish you'd never heard in your entire life

Hmm, I like most of my own entries...I'll single out any of my 3 Icelanders - there just was nothing there.

* Gone out completely in the quarter finals

Well I don't know how many times but I know I went completely out in my first go.

* Held a record low finish for a country

Again mobile wiki isn't great but I probably do somewhere.

* Entered a song that you thought was going to do well but failed miserably

Got all night, have you? Gotta single out Robyn Sherwell. I was so excited to be able to send it, I genuinely thought it could win. Crashed out in the QF. My own contest too.

* Chose an artist for the first time that has since been brought back

Lenny . Franziska Wiese being re-sent recently sticks out too. Probably some more.

* Sent an act that has gone to ESC or a NF after picking them

Tinkara and Elhaida. And yes, I cheered for both of them on the big nights. Oh, & EBU channels, if you're listening, some additions to that list could make Lisbon a great one

* Qualified through a round

Yes, 12 times and counting

* Reached a final

Yes, in 82, 83, 84, 87 and 88. Eight songs so far, out of 21.

* Got two or more countries into a final

Yes, in Snowdonia (Gibraltar and Germany), Hell (Estonia and New Zealand) and Le Hurel.

* Finished top 10

Once. 10th place with Kerli in Hell.

* Finished top 10 with more than one entry in the same contest

Obviously not.

* Held a record finish for a country

Bizarrely, with Lapland this edition. 15th in a SF. I'm going to hold onto that and forget the fact it has only been entered in three contests.

* Won a quarter final

YES! My one first place finish, in QF2 in Hell with New Zealand.

* Won the QF, SF and final

Who are we kidding here.

* Received a set of 12 points in the final

Certainly have. Not sure how many, but it's happened.

* Suffered a voting collapse

Hula Hula was robbed.

* Finished last

Twice in a row, Venice and Snowdonia.

* Entered a song including some rap

Yes.

* Sent a song you now seriously wish you'd never heard in your entire life

The Nina Pušlar song I sent for Berlin was enough to send anyone to sleep. Slovenia was a tough one though.

* Gone out completely in the quarter finals

Unfortunately, in ISS and Berlin. Adelén deserved better.

* Held a record low finish for a country

I was handed Australia in my first contest, and it utterly bombed. Thankfully aliyah took the record later on!

* Entered a song that you thought was going to do well but failed miserably

Every single contest.

* Chose an artist for the first time that has since been brought back

Nope

* Sent an act that has gone to ESC or a NF after picking them

Nope
